    "created_at": "2016-08-04T13:03:34Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-08-04T13:03:34Z",
    "body": "This is intentional, showing window title for `hidden-inset` would result in an ugly titlebar, because the titlebar is tall and the title text is small. Usually Mac apps would show a toolbar in titlebar, however since Electron doesn't support creating native toolbars, leaving an empty titlebar is the only option that does not look ugly.\n\nI'm closing this since it is a limitation of Electron.\n"
